com.vmware.nsx.upgrade

Class UpgradeFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.upgrade.UpgradeFactory

  • public class UpgradeFactory
extends Object
    UpgradeFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.upgrade package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
